<header class="hero-section">
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <div class="text-content">
        <h1 class="animate-fade-in">Hi, I'm <span class="gradient-text">Sanjkeet Jena</span></h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">Senior Software Development Engineer</h2>
        <p class="description animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
            Building scalable distributed systems and solving complex problems at Arcesium. 
