        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">
            <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Work</a>
            <a href="/Sanjkeet_resume_ep5.5.pdf" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Download CV</a>
        </div>
